  ('8131097e-9e96-462b-8229-b4b7c5de0c3a', 'Refine 2nd Edition', '数学Ｃ', '4', '4', 'Chapter 4', '5', '極限と連続 Q5（難）', 'x≠2 のとき f(x)=(x^2-5x+6)/(x-2) とする。f(x) が x=2 で連続になるように f(2) を定めると、その値はいくつか。', null, '{}'::jsonb, '[{"id":"csv_8131097e-9e96-462b-8229-b4b7c5de0c3a_question_title","type":"heading","page":"question","x":24,"y":24,"w":360,"h":36,"text":"極限と連続 Q5（難）"},{"id":"csv_8131097e-9e96-462b-8229-b4b7c5de0c3a_question_body","type":"question","page":"question","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":96,"text":"x≠2 のとき f(x)=(x^2-5x+6)/(x-2) とする。f(x) が x=2 で連続になるように f(2) を定めると、その値はいくつか。"},{"id":"csv_8131097e-9e96-462b-8229-b4b7c5de0c3a_question_choices","type":"text","page":"question","x":24,"y":184,"w":392,"h":92,"text":"A: -1\nB: 1\nC: 2"},{"id":"csv_8131097e-9e96-462b-8229-b4b7c5de0c3a_text_explanation","type":"text","page":"text","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":180,"text":"分子は (x-2)(x-3) と因数分解できるので、x≠2 では f(x)=x-3。よって lim_{x-\u003e2} f(x)=-1 であり、連続にするには f(2)=-1。Bは符号ミス、Cは見かけに引きずられた誤答。参照定理：連続の定義と除去可能な不連続"}]'::jsonb, '{"binder":"Refine 2nd Edition","note":"数学Ｃ","chapter":"4","section":"","textNumber":"4","textName":"Chapter 4","questionNumber":"5","questionName":"極限と連続 Q5（難）","contentText":"x≠2 のとき f(x)=(x^2-5x+6)/(x-2) とする。f(x) が x=2 で連続になるように f(2) を定めると、その値はいくつか。","contentHtml":"","notebookBlocks":[{"id":"csv_8131097e-9e96-462b-8229-b4b7c5de0c3a_question_title","type":"heading","page":"question","x":24,"y":24,"w":360,"h":36,"text":"極限と連続 Q5（難）"},{"id":"csv_8131097e-9e96-462b-8229-b4b7c5de0c3a_question_body","type":"question","page":"question","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":96,"text":"x≠2 のとき f(x)=(x^2-5x+6)/(x-2) とする。f(x) が x=2 で連続になるように f(2) を定めると、その値はいくつか。"},{"id":"csv_8131097e-9e96-462b-8229-b4b7c5de0c3a_question_choices","type":"text","page":"question","x":24,"y":184,"w":392,"h":92,"text":"A: -1\nB: 1\nC: 2"},{"id":"csv_8131097e-9e96-462b-8229-b4b7c5de0c3a_text_explanation","type":"text","page":"text","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":180,"text":"分子は (x-2)(x-3) と因数分解できるので、x≠2 では f(x)=x-3。よって li