  ('08a67ce6-da65-4295-acb6-9bce6a57dcc0', 'Refine 2nd Edition', '数学Ｃ', '6', '6', 'Chapter 6', '3', '積分法 Q3（中）', '区間 0≦x≦1 において、曲線 y=x と y=x^2 で囲まれる部分の面積を求めよ。', null, '{}'::jsonb, '[{"id":"csv_08a67ce6-da65-4295-acb6-9bce6a57dcc0_question_title","type":"heading","page":"question","x":24,"y":24,"w":360,"h":36,"text":"積分法 Q3（中）"},{"id":"csv_08a67ce6-da65-4295-acb6-9bce6a57dcc0_question_body","type":"question","page":"question","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":96,"text":"区間 0≦x≦1 において、曲線 y=x と y=x^2 で囲まれる部分の面積を求めよ。"},{"id":"csv_08a67ce6-da65-4295-acb6-9bce6a57dcc0_question_choices","type":"text","page":"question","x":24,"y":184,"w":392,"h":92,"text":"A: 1/6\nB: 1/3\nC: 1/2"},{"id":"csv_08a67ce6-da65-4295-acb6-9bce6a57dcc0_text_explanation","type":"text","page":"text","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":180,"text":"上が y=x、下が y=x^2 なので、面積は ∫_0^1(x-x^2)dx=[x^2/2-x^3/3]_0^1=1/6。Bは差を取らない誤り、Cは概形だけで見積もった誤答。参照定理：2曲線で囲まれた面積"}]'::jsonb, '{"binder":"Refine 2nd Edition","note":"数学Ｃ","chapter":"6","section":"","textNumber":"6","textName":"Chapter 6","questionNumber":"3","questionName":"積分法 Q3（中）","contentText":"区間 0≦x≦1 において、曲線 y=x と y=x^2 で囲まれる部分の面積を求めよ。","contentHtml":"","notebookBlocks":[{"id":"csv_08a67ce6-da65-4295-acb6-9bce6a57dcc0_question_title","type":"heading","page":"question","x":24,"y":24,"w":360,"h":36,"text":"積分法 Q3（中）"},{"id":"csv_08a67ce6-da65-4295-acb6-9bce6a57dcc0_question_body","type":"question","page":"question","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":96,"text":"区間 0≦x≦1 において、曲線 y=x と y=x^2 で囲まれる部分の面積を求めよ。"},{"id":"csv_08a67ce6-da65-4295-acb6-9bce6a57dcc0_question_choices","type":"text","page":"question","x":24,"y":184,"w":392,"h":92,"text":"A: 1/6\nB: 1/3\nC: 1/2"},{"id":"csv_08a67ce6-da65-4295-acb6-9bce6a57dcc0_text_explanation","type":"text","page":"text","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":180,"text":"上が y=x、下が y=x^2 なので、面積は ∫_0^1(x-x^2)dx=[x^2/2-x^3/3]_0^1=1/6。Bは差を取らない誤り、Cは概形だけで見積もった誤答。参照定理：2曲線で囲まれた面積"}],"answerType":"choice","answers":["A: 1/6"],"choices":["A: 1/6","B: 1/3","C: 1/2"],"explanatio