  ('c8042778-5f61-4d58-b26f-17d72c5b1ee7', 'Refine 2nd Edition', '数学Ｃ', '6', '6', 'Chapter 6', '5', '積分法 Q5（難）', '∫_{-1}^{2} |x-1| dx を求めよ。', null, '{}'::jsonb, '[{"id":"csv_c8042778-5f61-4d58-b26f-17d72c5b1ee7_question_title","type":"heading","page":"question","x":24,"y":24,"w":360,"h":36,"text":"積分法 Q5（難）"},{"id":"csv_c8042778-5f61-4d58-b26f-17d72c5b1ee7_question_body","type":"question","page":"question","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":96,"text":"∫_{-1}^{2} |x-1| dx を求めよ。"},{"id":"csv_c8042778-5f61-4d58-b26f-17d72c5b1ee7_question_choices","type":"text","page":"question","x":24,"y":184,"w":392,"h":92,"text":"A: 5/2\nB: 3/2\nC: 2"},{"id":"csv_c8042778-5f61-4d58-b26f-17d72c5b1ee7_text_explanation","type":"text","page":"text","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":180,"text":"x=1 で場合分けし、[-1,1] では |x-1|=1-x、[1,2] では |x-1|=x-1。∫_{-1}^{1}(1-x)dx+∫_{1}^{2}(x-1)dx=2+1/2=5/2。BやCは絶対値の分割不足。参照定理：絶対値を含む定積分の区間分割"}]'::jsonb, '{"binder":"Refine 2nd Edition","note":"数学Ｃ","chapter":"6","section":"","textNumber":"6","textName":"Chapter 6","questionNumber":"5","questionName":"積分法 Q5（難）","contentText":"∫_{-1}^{2} |x-1| dx を求めよ。","contentHtml":"","notebookBlocks":[{"id":"csv_c8042778-5f61-4d58-b26f-17d72c5b1ee7_question_title","type":"heading","page":"question","x":24,"y":24,"w":360,"h":36,"text":"積分法 Q5（難）"},{"id":"csv_c8042778-5f61-4d58-b26f-17d72c5b1ee7_question_body","type":"question","page":"question","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":96,"text":"∫_{-1}^{2} |x-1| dx を求めよ。"},{"id":"csv_c8042778-5f61-4d58-b26f-17d72c5b1ee7_question_choices","type":"text","page":"question","x":24,"y":184,"w":392,"h":92,"text":"A: 5/2\nB: 3/2\nC: 2"},{"id":"csv_c8042778-5f61-4d58-b26f-17d72c5b1ee7_text_explanation","type":"text","page":"text","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":180,"text":"x=1 で場合分けし、[-1,1] では |x-1|=1-x、[1,2] では |x-1|=x-1。∫_{-1}^{1}(1-x)dx+∫_{1}^{2}(x-1)dx=2+1/2=5/2。BやCは絶対値の分割不足。参照定理：絶対値を含む定積分の区間分割"}],"answerType":"choice","answers":["A: 5/2"],"choices":["A: 5/2","B: 3/2","C: 2"],"explanation":"x=1 で場合分けし、[-1,1] では |x-1|=1-x、[1,2] では |x-1|=x-1。∫_{-1}^{1}(1-x)dx+∫_{1}^{2}(x-1)dx=2+1/2=5/2。BやCは絶対値の分割不足。参照定理：絶対値を含む定積分の区間分割","deckId":"refine-math-c","subjectId":"refine-math-c","subjectLabel":"数学Ｃ","subjectName":"Mathematics C","seriesId":"review-2nd-edition","seriesLabel":"Refine 2nd Edition","sourceCsvId":"c8042778-5f61-4d58-b26f-17d72c5b1ee7","sourceApp":"The Review Manager CSV Import","status":"approved"}'::jsonb, 'approved', 'The Review Manager CSV Import', '{}'::jsonb, now(), now(), now(), now()),
  ('7dae22de-bb59-40e0-a314-a2efe9964812', 'Refine 2nd Edition', '数学Ｃ', '7', '7', 'Chapter 7', '1', '行列と行列式 Q1（易）', 'A=((1,2),(3,4)), B=((2,0),(1,-1)) とする。A+B を求めよ。', null, '{}'::jsonb, '[{"id":"csv_7dae22de-bb59-40e0-a314-a2efe9964812_question_title","type":"heading","page":"question","x":24,"y":24,"w":360,"h":36,"text":"行列と行列式 Q1（易）"},{"id":"csv_7dae22de-bb59-40e0-a314-a2efe9964812_question_body","type":"question","page":"question","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":96,"text":"A=((1,2),(3,4)), B=((2,0),(1,-1)) とする。A+B を求めよ。"},{"id":"csv_7dae22de-bb59-40e0-a314-a2efe9964812_question_choices","type":"text","page":"question","x":24,"y":184,"w":392,"h":92,"text":"A: ((3,2),(4,3))\nB: ((2,2),(3,-4))\nC: ((2,0),(1,-1))"},{"id":"csv_7dae22de-bb59-40e0-a314-a2efe9964812_text_explanation","type":"text","page":"text","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":180,"text":"行列の和は対応する成分どうしを足すので、((1+2,2+0),(3+1,4+(-1)))=((3,2),(4,3))。Bは成分対応を崩した誤り、CはBをそのまま写した誤答。参照定理：行列の和の定義"}]'::jsonb, '{"binder":"Refine 2nd Edition","note":"数学Ｃ","chapter":"7","section":"","textNumber":"7","textName":"Chapter 7","questionNumber":"1","questionName":"行列と行列式 Q1（易）","contentText":"A=((1,2),(3,4)), B=((2,0),(1,-1)) とする。A+B を求めよ。","contentHtml":"","notebookBlocks":[{"id":"csv_7dae22de-bb59-40e0-a314-a2efe9964812_question_title","type":"heading","page":"question","x":24,"y":24,"w":360,"h":36,"text":"行列と行列式 Q1（易）"},{"id":"csv_7dae22de-bb59-40e0-a314-a2efe9964812_question_body","type":"question","page":"question","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":96,"text":"A=((1,2),(3,4)), B=((2,0),(1,-1)) とする。A+B を求めよ。"},{"id":"csv_7dae22de-bb59-40e0-a314-a2efe9964812_question_choices","type":"text","page":"question","x":24,"y":184,"w":392,"h":92,"text":"A: ((3,2),(4,3))\nB: ((2,2),(3,-4))\nC: ((2,0),(1,-1))"},{"id":"csv_7dae22de-bb59-40e0-a314-a2efe9964812_text_explanation","type":"text","page":"text","x":24,"y":72,"w":392,"h":180,"text":"行列の和は対応する成分どうしを足すので、((1+2,2+0),(3+1,4+(-1)))=((3,2),(4,3))。Bは成分対応を崩した誤り、CはBをそのまま写した誤答。参照定理：行列の和の定義"}],"answerType":